data.name: AzureMapsAddressAutoComplete description
data.value: A PowerApps Component Framework (PCF) control for address autocomplete powered by Azure Maps. Provides intelligent address search, geocoding, and interactive map preview.
data.comment: Control description - matches description-key in manifest

data.name: azureMapsAddressSearchAutoComplete_Display_Key
data.comment: Display name for the main address search field

data.name: azureMapsAddressSearchAutoComplete_Desc_Key
data.value: The primary address field bound for autocomplete functionality. This field triggers the Azure Maps address search.
data.comment: Description for the main address search field

data.name: street_Desc_Key
data.value: The street address field to populate with the selected address street name and number.

data.name: city_Desc_Key
data.value: The city field to populate with the municipality from the selected address.

data.name: postalCode_Display_Key
data.comment: Display name for postal code field

data.name: postalCode_Desc_Key
data.value: The postal code or ZIP code field to populate from the selected address.

data.name: county_Desc_Key
data.value: The county or district field to populate from the selected address.

data.name: stateProvince_Desc_Key
data.value: The state, province, or region field to populate from the selected address.

data.name: stateProvinceCode_Display_Key
data.comment: Display name for state/province code field

data.name: stateProvinceCode_Desc_Key
data.value: The state or province code field (e.g., CA, TX, NY) to populate from the selected address.

data.name: country_Desc_Key
data.value: The country field to populate with the country name from the selected address.

data.name: countryCodeISO2_Display_Key
data.comment: Display name for ISO 3166-1 alpha-2 country code field

data.name: countryCodeISO2_Desc_Key
data.value: The ISO 3166-1 alpha-2 country code field (e.g., US, GB, DE) to populate from the selected address.
data.comment: Description for ISO2 country code field

data.name: countryCodeISO3_Display_Key
data.comment: Display name for ISO 3166-1 alpha-3 country code field

data.name: countryCodeISO3_Desc_Key
data.value: The ISO 3166-1 alpha-3 country code field (e.g., USA, GBR, DEU) to populate from the selected address.
data.comment: Description for ISO3 country code field

data.name: longitude_Desc_Key
data.value: The longitude coordinate field to populate with the geocoded location (decimal degrees).

data.name: latitude_Desc_Key
data.value: The latitude coordinate field to populate with the geocoded location (decimal degrees).

data.name: resultScore_Display_Key
data.comment: Display name for result score field

data.name: resultScore_Desc_Key
data.value: The confidence score field to populate with the geocoding match quality (0-1 scale).

data.name: defaultCountries_Display_Key
data.comment: Display name for default countries setting

data.name: defaultCountries_Desc_Key
data.value: Comma-separated list of ISO 3166-1 alpha-2 country codes to limit address search results (e.g., "US,CA,MX").

data.name: showMaps_Display_Key
data.comment: Display name for show maps toggle

data.name: showMaps_Desc_Key
data.value: Enable or disable the interactive map preview panel for address suggestions.

data.name: mapSize_Display_Key
data.comment: Display name for map size setting

data.name: mapSize_Desc_Key
data.value: The size of the map preview panel when displayed. Choose from Small, Medium, or Large.

data.name: mapSize_small_Desc_Key

data.comment: Description for small map size option

data.name: mapSize_medium_Desc_Key

data.comment: Description for medium map size option

data.name: mapSize_large_Desc_Key
